<Nav>
    <Left>
      <HiShoppingCart size={22} />
      <StyledLink to='/'>
        <Logo>SHOPSPREE</Logo>
      </StyledLink>
    </Left>
    <Center>
      <Search>
        <Input size={35} placeholder='Search here' />
        <AiOutlineSearch size={22} />
      </Search>
    </Center>
    <Right>
      <StyledLink to ='/register'>
        <MenuItem>
          REGISTER
        </MenuItem>
      </StyledLink>
      <StyledLink to ='/login'>
        <MenuItem>
          LOGIN
        </MenuItem>
      </StyledLink>
      <StyledLink to ='/cart'>
        <MenuItem>
          <Badge badgeContent={quantity} color='secondary' >
            <BsCart2 />
          </Badge>
        </MenuItem>
      </StyledLink>
    </Right>
  </Nav>
